title: Photo: PV Grand Prix continues Sunday
text: Photo: PV Grand Prix continues Sunday Prescott Valley - October 24, 2015Les Stukenberg/The Daily CourierDirt bikes, quads, UTV's and even a sidecar race in the first ever Prescott Valley Grand Prix in the fields in front of the PV Event Center Saturday. Racing action continues Sunday beginning at 8 a.m. Dirt bikes, quads, UTV's and even a sidecar, race in the first ever Prescott Valley Grand Prix in the fields in front of the PV Event Center Saturday.
